    {
      "instruction": "<p>Slice your <strong>cherry tomatoes</strong> in half</p><p>Dissolve your <strong>chicken stock mix</strong> and <strong>tomato paste </strong>in 200ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[275ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[350ml]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>– this is your <strong>tomato stock</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1678174275236-x200.jpg",
