            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the onion and peppers are starting to soften, add the <strong>tomato stock</strong> to the pan with the <strong>halved cherry tomatoes </strong>and<strong> dried oregano </strong>and cook for 2-3 min or until thickened</p><p>Once thickened, stir the <strong>cooked wholewheat tortiglioni</strong> through the tomato sauce and season generously with<strong> black pepper</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1678174284210-x200.jpg",
