          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, grate your <strong>cheddar cheese</strong></p><p>Drain your <strong>mozzarella</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper (squeeze as much liquid out as you can)</p><p>Tear the <strong>drained mozzarella</strong> into rough, bite-sized pieces</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
